Project Bureau — ATF1502BE Logic Block A

Project Bureau aims at documenting the bitstream format of Microchip ATF15xx CPLDs. This is a work in progress.

Macrocell Configuration Bitmap

Logic block A uses 480 fuses at 15360..15840 for macrocells MC1, MC2, MC3, MC4, MC5, MC6, MC7, MC8, MC9, MC10, MC11, MC12, MC13, MC14, MC15, MC16.
